OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fine day for many with
OL,6,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells.
OL,7,FFeeling warm in the south and east. A
OL,8,Ffew showers possible in the north,
OL,9,Fahead of rain and stronger winds
OL,10,Freaching Northern Ireland and western
OL,11,FScotland in the afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWindy in the north with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of rain this evening, heavy
OL,15,Fat times, then turning drier
OL,16,Fovernight. Cloud reaching southern
OL,17,Fareas later, bringing coastal and hill
OL,18,Ffog to the southwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
