OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloud and patchy rain
OL,6,Fclearing the far south through the
OL,7,Fday. Largely dry elsewhere with sunny
OL,8,Fspells. Remaining windy in the
OL,9,Fnortheast. Cool in the northwest, warm
OL,10,Fin the southeast.
